            effects: [],
            description: "Cyberarm Option. Armored knuckles. A Medium Melee Weapon (2d6 damage, 2 ROF) that can be successfully concealed without a Check. When wielded as a weapon, user can't hold anything in this arm's hand. Can be installed as the only piece of Cyberware in a meat arm. See p.364.",
        ),
        (
            slug: "cyberarm_cyberdeck",
            display_name: "Cyberdeck (in Cyberarm)",
